For the middle section, here are a few ideas to make the event flyer more engaging:

Interactive Activity Highlights
Add icons or images representing activities (face painting, bouncy castles, arts & crafts, games) with short descriptions.

Special Guests or Performances
Showcase a banner with photos or illustrations of entertainers (magicians, clowns, mascots).

Event Schedule Preview
Include a mini timetable highlighting exciting activities at different times.

Call-to-Action Button
Add a colorful "Get Tickets Now!" or "Join Us!" button for sign-ups or RSVPs.

Fun Quote or Slogan
Include a catchy phrase like "Where Imagination Comes to Life!" in playful typography.

Would you like me to mock up one of these ideas for you?